<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Actually for a while these could drop off of normal cenos..they fixed that in patch though.  Grand Cenobite drops it in Frontier Mountains..hes like any other rare there and wanders a set path.</font></td></tr></table>
