<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Silanya Velve</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-07 17:36:26</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This item is dropped off the Grand Burynai Cenobite in the NW corner of the Frontier Mountains zone.  It is a triggered spawn, which means you have to kill the named NPC's in the zone, the computer will then roll a random number to see which NPC will spawn next.  Most of the named NPCs will spawn in the NW corner near the Temple of Droga.  I hope this helps!<BR>
<BR>
~High Priestess Silanya Velve<BR>
~Erollisi Marr</font></td></tr></table>
