<BR>
Just to give you an idea of the value of this belt. <BR>
<BR>
I play a ranger and got this belt, as many has stated from the Burynai Grand Cenobite in FM. Anyways, I was going to put it on my secondary char, a lvl 18 Cleric, 'cause I thought it was a rather nifty belt for him.<BR>
<BR>
Then I learned that this is actually the best preplane belt for cleric, some even says it's better, so I got a little trade for it....This ranger finally got his FBSS. <BR>
<BR>
So, I'm happy :)<BR>
