<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>It's small races ONLY, that's why Humans and Erudites can't wear it.  High Elves and Wood Elves can wear medium AND small armor, hence why they can wear this in addition to the small-only races.</font></td></tr></table>
